                "invention-title": [
                    "Peak shaving system and peak shaving method for high-temperature gas cooled reactor nuclear power unit",
                    "一种高温气冷堆核电机组的调峰系统及调峰方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of nuclear power regulation and control, in particular to a peak regulation system and peak regulation method for a high-temperature gas cooled reactor nuclear power unit, which utilizes the advantage of high parameter of a high-temperature gas cooled reactor, considers the high-temperature operating environment and high-efficiency hydrogen production requirements and advantages of a solid oxide water electrolysis hydrogen production system and combines a seawater desalination system. The whole peak regulation process is completed while heat output of the nuclear island is not changed, nuclear island equipment life loss caused by frequent peak regulation of a unit is reduced by means of the fuel consumption characteristic of the nuclear island, meanwhile, the low-carbon process of an energy system is promoted by means of the advantages of a hydrogen energy storage system, and in addition, the multiple operation modes are provided, so that the energy utilization rate is increased. On the premise of considering heat supply, various forms of energy supply such as peak regulation, stable fresh water supply and hydrogen preparation can be achieved, the progress of multi-element energy supply of the nuclear power unit is effectively promoted, and the nuclear power unit operation economic benefits are expected to be improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种高温气冷堆核电机组的调峰系统及调峰方法，核电调控技术领域，利用高温气冷堆高参数的优势，考虑到固体氧化物电解水制氢系统高温运行环境以及高效制氢的需求和优点，结合海水淡化系统，实现了不改变核岛热量输出的同时完成了整个调峰过程，利用核岛燃料消耗特性，降低了机组频繁调峰导致的核岛设备寿命损耗，同时利用氢储能系统的优势推进了能源体系低碳化进程，此外本发明提出的多种运行模式，在考虑到供热的前提下，可以实现调峰、稳定淡水供给、氢气制备等多种形式的能量供给，有效推动了核电机组多元供能的进展，有望提高核电机组运行经济效益。"
                }
            ]
